      • parameters

        private java.util.Map<java.lang.String,TypedDefaultValue> parameters
        Required parameters of the function.

        The map should not be null, but it can be empty if there are no parameters.

        • Key: key used to identify the parameter
        • Value: description of the parameter (see TypedDefaultValue)
        Since:
        version 1
        See Also:
        FunctionCall.parameters

      • returnValues

        private java.util.Map<java.lang.String,DataType> returnValues
        Return values of the function.

        The map should not be null, but it can be empty if there is no return value.

        • Key: name/id of the return value
        • Value: DataType of the returned value
        Since:
        version 1
        See Also:
        FunctionReturn.data
